name: Clytie
description: Clytie is associated with more than 700+ global brands and over 170+ countries around the world. When members shop online on Clytie App and Web platforms, Clytie rewards users by CLY tokens and a cashback rate of up to 85%. Users can level up their membership to get rewards up to x3.5. Each level will need to hold a corresponding amount of CLY for bronze, silver, titanium, gold, and platinum levels.
